episodes.title: 12-Year-Old Girl from Satanic Sex Cult Gives Birth to Stepfather's Child
episodes.description: Ta’za endured unimaginable abuse in a satanic sex cult from age 4, suffering at the hands of her mother and stepfather. After giving birth at 12, she seeks her 18-year-old daughter. Despite her family's dismissal as "crazy," evidence from lie detector tests and medical records supports her claims. Her story sheds light on the trauma faced by abused women and raises awareness about the horrific abuses suffered by vulnerable girls.
